replyContent: Hi Elizabeth, you can print via wireless but Android requires that you install the appropriate Print Service Plugin (akin to a printer driver in the windows world). So, if you have an HP printer, you'd need to install the HP Printer Service Plugin. Once installed, tap the share icon, then Share/Print.

replyContent: Hi Sabine - sorry to disappoint! We have not added the Print & Ship feature to the Android app, and don't have it on our current roadmap. You can always print the strip at your local photo finisher (Walgreens, etc) for a more professional print.
